race.comment: Lots of win chances. REMEMBER POPPY (4) has run well in three runs since a win and looks close to finding another. On speed and fought on well last time and expected to take beating again. LEGACY BEL (5) is another who continues to race well. Has never missed the frame from five starts at the trip including maiden win. Just missed out last time and despite the draw rates a leading player. TRAK CHILLER (7) resumed from a spell over 1100m and powered home late to just miss. Fitter and can go one better. JUICE BOX (3) is better than last start on soft ground. Has good early pace and the claim here and can give a sight.
